Gnome15 Indicator
=================

Allows control and monitoring of the Gnome15 desktop service using the Indicator
specification from the Ayatana project. Can be used to launch the configuration
user interface, as well as show the current service status and select the visible
screen.

Installation
============

See the 'INSTALL' file.

How to report bugs
==================

See http://tanktarta.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/gnome15
